foia:ComplexResponseTimeIncrementsSectio.foia:FootnoteText: The FOIA Tracking System currently used by EEOC does not have the capability to track complex and simple requests separately. All non-expedited requests are shown on chart VII.B., simple requests.

foia:OldestPendingRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: The Los Angeles Office did not have any pending FOIA request at the end of the fiscal year. The Washington Field Office had only eight oldest requests ending. The second oldest request for the Memphis District Office was tolled for four days. The seventh oldest request for OLC was tolled for two days, and the tenth oldest was tolled for six days.

foia:OldestPendingConsultationSection.foia:FootnoteText: EEOC had no consultations with other agencies or components during Fiscal Year 2013.
